---

<BaseLayout {title} {description} schemaJsonLd={schemaJsonLd}>

  <!-- ══ HERO (navy) ══ -->
  <Hero
    h1="Accounting Services in Singapore"
    h1Accent="for Small Businesses"
    subhead="Fixed monthly fees. No surprises. Your books, payroll and financial statements handled remotely by a Financial Controller with 15+ years of experience, so you can get back to running your business."
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Book a free consultation', href: '/contact/' }}
    secondaryCta={{ label: 'Get a fixed quote', href: '/contact/' }}
    trustItems={["Xero & QuickBooks","SFRS-ready books","15+ years' experience","Serving Singapore SMEs remotely"]}
  />

  <!-- ══ STATS (gold) ══ -->
  <StatsBanner stats={[
    { value: "15+",  label: "Years' experience" },
    { value: "28%",  label: "Faster financial close" },
    { value: "S$90", label: "Starting from per month" },
    { value: "100%", label: "Cloud-based delivery" },
  ]} />

  <!-- ══ SPLIT 1: What services? (white, text left) ══ -->
  <SplitSection
    eyebrow="Core Services"
    heading="What accounting services do small businesses in Singapore need?"
    imageAlt="Accountant reviewing Xero bookkeeping dashboard"
    placeholderLabel="Accountant at desk reviewing Xero dashboard — clean modern Singapore office"
    placeholderIconPath="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25"
    variant="white" flip={false}
  >
    <AnswerBlock>
      <p>Most Singapore small businesses need a few core things handled well: bookkeeping, SFRS-compliant financial statements, payroll with CPF, and clear monthly management reports. Get these right and your records stay accurate, your statutory accounts are ready, and you have numbers you can actually use to run the business.</p>
    </AnswerBlock>
    <p>You don't need a full finance department. You need the essentials done correctly and on time. Everything most SMEs require sits inside one fixed monthly fee, so nothing slips through the cracks and you always know what you're paying.</p>
    <a href="/accounting-services-singapore/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-navy text-white text-sm font-600 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy-deep transition-colors mt-2">
      Explore services
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
    </a>
  </SplitSection>

  <!-- ══ SERVICES GRID (navy) ══ -->
  <section class="relative bg-navy py-24 lg:py-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[900px] h-[500px] rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(220,163,60,0.06) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
      <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-[0.035]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs><pattern id="dots-svc" width="28" height="28" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="14" cy="14" r="1.2" fill="#DAA035"/></pattern></defs>
        <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#dots-svc)"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="relative section-inner">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <div class="eyebrow-dark mb-5">What We Do</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl text-white max-w-xl mx-auto">Six services. One fixed monthly fee.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {services.map((svc) => (
          <ServiceCard title={svc.title} blurb={svc.blurb} href={svc.href} dark={true} iconPath={svc.icon} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ MINI CTA (navy) ══ -->
  <MiniBanner text="Not sure what services your business needs? Book a free 15-minute assessment call." ctaLabel="Book free call" ctaHref="/contact/" variant="navy" />

  <!-- ══ SPLIT 2: In-house vs outsource (light-bg, image left) ══ -->
  <SplitSection
    eyebrow="Cost Comparison"
    heading="Should you hire an in-house accountant or outsource?"
    imageAlt="Cost comparison: in-house salary vs outsourced fixed fee"
    placeholderLabel="Split graphic — in-house S$3,000+/month vs fixed outsourced fee"
    placeholderIconPath="M12 3v17.25m0 0c-1.472 0-2.882.265-4.185.75M12 20.25c1.472 0 2.882.265 4.185.75M18.75 4.97A48.416 48.416 0 0012 4.5c-2.291 0-4.545.16-6.75.47m13.5 0c1.01.143 2.01.317 3 .52m-3-.52l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031.352 5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L18.75 4.97zm-16.5.52c.99-.203 1.99-.377 3-.52m0 0l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031.352 5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L5.25 4.97z"
    variant="light" flip={true}
  >
    <AnswerBlock>
      <p>For most small businesses in Singapore, outsourcing is cheaper and safer than hiring in-house. A full-time accountant costs a monthly salary plus CPF, leave and software, often S$3,000+ a month, and is idle when transaction volume is low. Outsourcing gives you the same expertise for a fraction of the cost.</p>
    </AnswerBlock>
    <p>Hire in-house and you pay salary, CPF, benefits, software and training, then carry the risk yourself if that person leaves or makes an error.</p>
    <p>Outsource to us and you get one fixed fee, a dedicated qualified accountant, compliant software, and continuity you never have to manage. Scale the service up or down as the business grows.</p>
  </SplitSection>

  <!-- ══ MAIN GOLD CTA ══ -->
  <CTASection
    variant="gold"
    heading="Get a fixed quote in one free call."
    subtext="No obligation, no jargon. We'll assess your needs and send a clear monthly price within 24 hours."
    primaryLabel="Get a Free Quote"
    primaryHref="/contact/"
    secondaryLabel="See pricing"
    secondaryHref="/pricing/"
  />

  <!-- ══ SPLIT 3: Remote delivery (white, text left) ══ -->
  <SplitSection
    eyebrow="How We Work"
    heading="How do you deliver Singapore accounting services remotely?"
    imageAlt="Remote accountant on cloud accounting software"
    placeholderLabel="Laptop with Xero open, secure cloud upload, video call — modern remote accounting"
    placeholderIconPath="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 004.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 001.332-7.257 3 3 0 00-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 00-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 002.25 15z"
    variant="white" flip={false}
  >
    <AnswerBlock>
      <p>We work entirely in the cloud using Xero, secure document sharing and scheduled video calls. Because we operate remotely with lower overhead, our fees are lower than a traditional Singapore firm's, while every filing still meets ACRA, IRAS and SFRS requirements. You get the same compliance, less cost.</p>
    </AnswerBlock>
    <p>Remote doesn't mean hands-off. You get a named accountant, real-time access to your numbers on Xero, monthly reports, and direct answers when you have a question. Your records stay confidential and encrypted at every step.</p>
    <p>Founder Mehdi Javed has managed accounting operations for SMEs and logistics businesses across Pakistan, the UAE and the United States, so your books are in experienced hands, wherever they're kept.</p>
  </SplitSection>

  <!-- ══ SPLIT 4: How to choose (light-bg, image right) ══ -->
  <SplitSection
    eyebrow="Choosing Right"
    heading="How do you choose the right accountant for your business?"
    imageAlt="Three criteria for choosing an accountant in Singapore"
    placeholderLabel="Three criteria cards: Compliance, Transparent pricing, Direct access"
    placeholderIconPath="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z"
    variant="light" flip={true}
  >
    <AnswerBlock>
      <p>Three things matter most. Genuine local compliance knowledge across ACRA, IRAS, GST and SFRS. Pricing you can see before you sign. And direct access to a qualified person instead of a rotating call centre. A good accountant files on time, explains your numbers, and flags problems before they turn into penalties.</p>
    </AnswerBlock>
    <p>Most Singapore firms hide their fees and their people. With us, you know exactly what you pay and exactly who handles your account. You talk to Mehdi, not a queue.</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-navy text-white text-sm font-600 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy-deep transition-colors mt-2">
      Get a Quote <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
    </a>
  </SplitSection>

  <!-- ══ MINI CTA (light) ══ -->
  <MiniBanner text="Transparent pricing, published up front. No locked tiers, no surprise add-ons at year-end." ctaLabel="See pricing" ctaHref="/pricing/" variant="light" />

  <!-- ══ PRICING (navy) ══ -->
  <section class="relative bg-navy py-24 lg:py-28 overflow-hidden">
