    variant="light" flip={true}
  >
    <AnswerBlock>
      <p>Because you get a qualified Financial Controller, transparent fixed pricing, and direct personal service, not a faceless retainer. Mehdi Javed brings 15+ years of multi-entity finance experience, an Executive MBA in Accounting &amp; Finance, and a track record of 28% faster financial close and 10% cost reduction.</p>
    </AnswerBlock>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mt-2">
